data.description: Fantastic Home in sought after Brandonwood Estates in Keller ISD...You do not want to miss this opportunity.  Originally 3 bedroom floor plan but original owner had 3rd bedroom opened up to make the perfect study. Easy conversion to get back to a true 3 bedroom! The floorplan has one of the largest family rooms and kitchens in the neighborhood. Space in all the right places. Bedrooms sizes allow for largest of furniture. Light and bright throughout. The Open floorplan makes this home feel so roomy yet still so cozy. Icing on the cake is the fabulous covered patio you will be wanting that first cup of coffee on every morning and the backyard perfect for that garden you have always wanted.  PLEASE COME SEE...you will not be disappointed. AC and Hot water heater replaced last 2 years. Come make this home YOUR own with YOUR special touch. Home priced to allow the new Owners to personalize.Conveniently located to shopping and restaurants.
